Zero point energy                ...      0.44858289 Eh     281.49 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.02149644 Eh      13.49 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
